column2: b'Super Doll Licca-chan: Licca-chan Zettai Zetsumei! Doll Knights no Kiseki'

b'A fun day at the amusement park is interrupted when the evil witch Dana is reawakened. Queen Yae has sent her after Rika and only the Doll Knights can stop this threat. Meanwhile, Dai and the others must deal with other dangers. \n\n(Source: ANN)'
